author: Maggie Pehanick
title: Carrie Underwood and Keith Urban Singing "The Fighter" Will Get You Through Anything
text:
Carrie Underwood Performance Video at the 2017 Grammys Carrie Underwood and Keith Urban Singing "The Fighter" Will Get You Through Anything February 12, 2017 by Maggie Pehanick 513 Shares 
Carrie Underwood and Keith Urban need to get it together and become the modern Donny and Marie already (only, you know, not related). They sound so good together, as evidenced by their performance of "The Fighter" at the Grammys on Sunday. Take a look!
